oai_dc:dc.dc:description: R.B. Johnson house, 825 N. Fifth Avenue, Knoxville, TN. Ca. 1903. Submitted ID: Originally built as the W.B. Trent house in 1890 from George F. Barber plans. The original number was 89 N. Fifth Avenue and was renumbered to 825 ca. 1892.
